features.text:
Name: (Lim In-seok) 
in suk Lim.        
Stage name: 林性遇

Born in Seoul in 1970.
--
Solo Exhibition - 1996~2021__Suwon, Songtan, Busan, Ginza, Japan.                                                                      
Pyeongtaek, Seoul Arts Center, Jeju Island, etc.

Most of the group - 1992~2021__ Souleum 3 members. Former member of the International Association of Foot Foot Painters. Records of those who stand up.         Former Daegu Art Association for the Disabled.
                            Former Korean Art Association for the Disabled. Daejeon Brush Love.
                            Lisu Gallery, Ansan Nude Croquis, etc.
200 times outside.

All overseas - 2002~2021__Portugal, Turkey, Uzbekistan,
                           Egypt, India, Fukuoka/Ginza, Zurich, Japan,
                           Paris, New York, LA and many others



He is currently a full member of the World Oral Conversational Association.
     Regular member of the Korean Art Association for the Disabled, etc.
    
Website: https://artinsuk.creatorlink.net/
E-mail: swinsuk@hanmail.net
